    "Again, it is stressed that small steps are important, even if you go outside for only a few minutes each day.",
    "Another question ChatGPT has been asked is how to deal with traumatic images.",
    "The chatbot suggests two techniques: mindfulness and cognitive restructuring.",
    "To the feedback that \"I can't just observe painful images impassivelyˮ, it replies that not everyone can use all the techniques and suggests others.",
    "It promptly suggests another technique, namely self-compassion, and adds that it can take time to find the strategy that works best for coping with trauma."
